=== 参数 ===

{| class="wikitable"
! style="text-align:left" | Parameter
! style="text-align:left" | Usage
|-
! style="text-align:left" | prison_name
| Name of the facility
|-
! style="text-align:left" | image
| A photograph of the facility.  Use wiki image syntax.
|-
! style="text-align:left" | caption
| To go with the image
|-
! style="text-align:left" | location
| City, state, province, etc.
|-
! style="text-align:left" | coordinates
| Use {{tlx|coord|...|display{{=}}inline,title}}
|-
! style="text-align:left" | status
| "Operational" or "Closed"
|-
! style="text-align:left" | classification
| Security class, e.g. "Minimum", "Maximum",  "Minimum to medium", etc.
|-
! style="text-align:left" | capacity
| Maximum operating capacity of the facility
|-
! style="text-align:left" | population
| Actual inmate population
|-
! style="text-align:left" | populationdate
| Effective date of the "population" figure, above
|-
! style="text-align:left" | opened
| Year or date the facility began operating, Use {{Tl|Start date}}
|-
! style="text-align:left" | closed
| Year or date the facility closed
|-
! style="text-align:left" | managed_by
| Company that manages the facility.
|-
! style="text-align:left" | director <span style="font-weight: normal">or</span> governor <span style="font-weight: normal">or</span> warden
| Name of the warden or other individual responsible for day-to-day operations.
|-
! style="text-align:left" | prisoners
| Any notable prisoners. Separate by commas or line breaks.
|}

